## ğŸ› Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

**"OpenAI API key not provided"**
```bash
export OPENAI_API_KEY='your-api-key'
```

**"Module 'openai' not found"**
```bash
pip install openai
```

**"Could not load source files"**
- Ensure file paths in findings are relative to `--base-path`
- Check file permissions

